{"tid":1051161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美女師の特殊性教育　與11歲男生床戰百回惹到女友","createTime":"2019-03-07T11:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T12:17:47.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80339e28607f3b903a720af0139836ee5bf87480","tid":1051161,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"美國密西根州一名38歲特教女老師溫菲爾德(Heather Winfield)，被指控對一名11歲男生傳授「特殊性教育」，甚至床戰百回，該案在近日開庭審理。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，溫菲爾德在2016年7月，首次對這名11歲男生性侵，地點就在溫菲爾德的家中。男生也指出，他與老師不只在家裡，還在露營地、賓館等處進行「特殊性教育」。警方也蒐集到賓館收據和財力證明，表示女老師曾在3個月內租過16間房，更稱女老師和男生床戰1000回，但之後下修為100回。<br />\n<br />\n據悉兩人的「姦情」會被曝光，原因是男生的前女友看到男生的臉書上，留有與女老師的曖昧訊息，進而報警，溫菲爾德的教職工作也一度被暫停，之後離職。男生現年14歲，他除了承認與溫菲爾德的姦情，還加碼指控溫菲爾德搞3P。<br />\n<br />\n不過溫菲爾德的辯護律師沃達(Matt Wojda)，否認溫菲爾德性侵與勾引未成年者的指控，也否認3P指控。沃達強調，溫菲爾德和老公原本想要挽救這一名邊緣少年，甚至想要收為養子，但少年變得越來越暴力，讓溫菲爾德打消念頭。溫菲爾德和老公育有2女1子，從她的社群網路消息看來，全家目前都住在一起。<br />\n<br />\n該案仍持續開庭審理，若溫菲爾德罪成，最重恐面臨無期徒刑。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/14gLGDPO7HsXK0/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F14gLGDPO7HsXK0%2Fsource.gif&h=5f6c8503&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c300716ecc04d5242d3fdbb93773a4fbde241e9d","tid":1051161,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/suarez-chelsea.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoateallthepies.tv%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F11%2Fsuarez-chelsea.gif&h=ed56b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b91fb8471dac396d0a9a019ce9847d5ce81ec938","tid":1051161,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"3p犯法㗎原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8e912d322aa3fa4b5f35bc351482de67d29565","tid":1051161,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMQuthW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMQuthW.gif&h=5ca0c110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b67ba0fab700debdf9cfd95663c788c20abba07e","tid":1051161,"uid":27305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"54d1b9ed4d6d8ea2c4ea3d1c30764cd10def3830","tid":1051161,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b67ba0fab700debdf9cfd95663c788c20abba07e","tid":1051161,"uid":27305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QANdaAJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQANdaAJ.jpg&h=f96ff166&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba3e1bb3f5fd8e13e125a1326b7155b4d1076aec","tid":1051161,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:40:17.000Z","msg":"條女好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"d85d8154f87f112c681c2ef2da75362df736c140","tid":1051161,"uid":59848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"大家冷靜 睇定啲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798baac73946bac680a2c7d97fcedaa0ffbdd4c3","tid":1051161,"uid":33438,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9309ccb63d4595df706b21761f133c417675efcc","tid":1051161,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"798baac73946bac680a2c7d97fcedaa0ffbdd4c3","tid":1051161,"uid":33438,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0aaba0f743d4a72d4865aca11be77db3996859d"